Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.25,0:07:25.22,text,,0,0,0,,{\an6\bord2\blur5\shad0\3c&H1D1F25&\pos(1246,550)}逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.25,0:07:25.22,text,,0,0,0,,{\an6\bord2\blur5\shad0\3c&H1D1F25&\pos(1246,601)}掏钱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.50,0:07:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,逃不了!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.56,0:07:40.02,text,,0,0,0,,{\an6\bord2\blur5\shad0\3c&H1D1F25&\pos(760,505)}怎么办?
